title: Boyce Avenue discography (Current as of April 20, 2014)
description:
This is Boyce Avenue's full discography as of April 20, 2014. It includes every 

album of covers and originals, as well as the "Live in Los Angeles" album. It 

also includes the single "Your Biggest Fan" and the currently released songs from

their new EP, "No Limits"




Subscribe to their YouTube channel.
